title: How close are we to full movie generation from a technical standpoint?
text: With DALL-E and similar things popping up, the ability to generate things accurately based on text prompts, etc. how soon will we be able to generate things like entire screenplays that are indistinguishable from others written by people, sophisticated acting performances or just straight up entire movies being generated? What will that progression look like? Are we talking years? Decades?
